# SIXMEN Data Safety

> ADR-010 · `docs/erp/phases/GD0_Nen_tang/ERD.md` §5 · `docs/erp/phases/GD1_Kho_SX/ERD.md` §20 · `docs/erp/core/04_Architecture.md` §11.6

## Purpose

Prevent data loss, unsafe deletion, unsafe purge, and accidental production damage.

## Memory Scope

This rule must keep active:

- **Scope governed:** cấm destructive ops prod, append-only movement/audit, soft delete ≠ purge, DB user separation.
- **Canonical context:** ADR-010 · `docs/erp/phases/GD0_Nen_tang/ERD.md` §5 · `docs/erp/phases/GD1_Kho_SX/ERD.md` §20 · `docs/erp/core/04_Architecture.md` §11.6.
- **Required project memory:** không `DELETE`/`TRUNCATE`/`DROP` prod · correction = cancel/reversal/adjustment/exception · `sixmen_app` / `sixmen_report` / `sixmen_migration` roles.
- **Deprecated / rejected:** hard delete core ERP · rewrite movement/audit history · auto-purge MVP · raw SQL khuyến khích DELETE prod.
- **Applies to:** DB, migration, backend service, import/export, report, release, production data.
- **Does not apply to:** docs-only tasks (không relax guard khi task sau đụng data).
- **Conflict handling:** không skill/role rule nào override data safety; defer `sixmen-governance` cho Human Owner gate.
- **Stop condition:** yêu cầu xóa/purge prod · drop/rename schema · bypass audit · đổi retention.

## Always apply

Any task touching database, migration, backend service, import/export, report, release, or production data.

## Guardrails

- **Never** run manual `DELETE` / `TRUNCATE` / `DROP` on production.
- **Never** add raw SQL examples that encourage direct production `DELETE`.
- **Never** hard delete core ERP data.
- Soft delete does **not** mean physical purge.
- Do **not** auto-purge: `inventory_movements`, `material_inventory_movements`, `activity_log`, PO/GRN/QC/production/transfer/adjustment documents, user/branch/legal entity/warehouse core data.
- Movement/audit tables are **append-only**: `inventory_movements`, `material_inventory_movements`, `activity_log`, audit/event logs.
- **Không** `UPDATE` / `DELETE` movement hoặc audit để “sửa lỗi nghiệp vụ” — không hard delete core ERP data.
- Business correction → **cancel / reversal / adjustment / exception** only.
- Future purge **must** have: whitelist, dry-run, batch limit, max affected rows, reference check, audit, approval, backup/snapshot, rollback plan.
- **MVP:** do **not** build purge/archive jobs — policy only.

## DB user separation

| User | Role |
|------|------|
| `sixmen_app` | Normal app read/write |
| `sixmen_report` | Read-only reporting (`pgsql_reporting`) |
| `sixmen_migration` | Deploy/migration only |
| `sixmen_maintenance` | Future purge/archive only |
| `postgres` / admin | **Never** used by app |

## Stop conditions

Stop and ask Human Owner if task:

- asks to delete production data;
- asks to drop/rename columns/tables;
- asks to bypass audit;
- asks to purge movement/audit/core ERP records;
- changes data retention behavior.
